name: QRY-0001
sql:
SELECT count(*) AS `Total Customers`
  FROM `tabCustomer` AS `tabCustomer`
 LIMIT 100
title: Total Customers Visual Query

name: QRY-0084
sql:
SELECT `tabSales Invoice Item`.item_code AS `Item Code`,
       `tabCustomer`.type_of_customer AS `Type Of Customer`,
       sum(`tabSales Invoice Item`.qty) AS `Refills`,
       count(DISTINCT `tabSales Invoice`.customer) AS `Customer`,
       sum(`tabSales Invoice Item`.qty) / count(DISTINCT `tabSales Invoice`.customer) AS `Refill Rate`
  FROM `tabSales Invoice Item` AS `tabSales Invoice Item`
 INNER JOIN `tabSales Invoice` AS `tabSales Invoice`
    ON `tabSales Invoice Item`.parent = `tabSales Invoice`.name
 INNER JOIN `tabCustomer` AS `tabCustomer`
    ON `tabSales Invoice`.customer = `tabCustomer`.name
 WHERE `tabSales Invoice Item`.item_code LIKE '%%refill%%'
 GROUP BY `tabSales Invoice Item`.item_code,
          `tabCustomer`.type_of_customer
 LIMIT 10000000
title: Average # of refill SKUs per Customer TypeÂ

name: QRY-0005
sql:
SELECT `tabCustomer`.lead_source AS `Lead Source`,
       count(*) AS `Total Customers`,
       (count(*) / SUM(COUNT(*)) OVER ()) * 100 AS `Referral Rate`
  FROM `tabCustomer` AS `tabCustomer`
 GROUP BY `tabCustomer`.lead_source
 LIMIT 10000000

name: QRY-0004
sql:

       count(*) AS `Total Customers`
  FROM `tabCustomer` AS `tabCustomer`

name: QRY-0015
sql:
SELECT (sum(CASE WHEN (`tabCustomer`.lead_source = 'Customer Referral') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / count(*)) * 100 AS `Referral Rate`
  FROM `tabCustomer` AS `tabCustomer`
 LIMIT 100
title: Customer Referral RateÂ  Â

name: QRY-0012
sql:
SELECT count(*) AS `Total Customers`,
       sum(CASE WHEN (`tabCustomer`.status = 'Active') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `Active Customers`,
       (sum(CASE WHEN (`tabCustomer`.status = 'Active') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) / count(*)) * 100 AS `Referral rate`,
       count(*) - sum(CASE WHEN (`tabCustomer`.status = 'Active') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS `New Customers`
  FROM `tabCustomer` AS `tabCustomer`
 LIMIT 10000000
title: Referral Rate Visual Query

name: QRY-0016
sql:

 GROUP BY `tabCustomer`.referral_company
 LIMIT 100
title: Franchise wise Customers
